| `/api/dashboard/rankings` | GET | Get ranked sessions (query params: `limit`, `sort_by`, `order`) |
| `/api/dashboard/session/{session_id}` | GET | Get detailed breakdown for one session |
| `/api/dashboard/trends` | GET | Get score history for trend chart |

